    "description": {
      "content": "The AirLabs Cities Database API returns a list of global cities filterable by IATA city_code, ISO 2 country_code, or selected fields. City data complements and extends the AirLabs airports dataset for travel search, mapping, and geocoding experiences.\n\nContact Support:\n Name: AirLabs Support",
